{"tid":302053,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪間間學校嘅校務處都係收錢返黎玩／屌鳩D學生？","createTime":"2017-06-29T05:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T15:43:53.000Z","uid":11477,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc11eaa2dc9ca659fe516e7057afe02a42be33b8","tid":302053,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"啱啱打過去問野<br />\n成班都唔撚知係咪心理變態<br />\n問你少少野又西你面又要唔耐煩咁<br />\n好似殺撚左你全家<br />\n<br />\n之前同朋友打算報義工團<br />\n我地兩個係衰仔<br />\n人地話個日5點dead<br />\n我地又真係4:55分到<br />\n去到個到我地諗住交<br />\n去到門口仲有個女仔加入我地deadline fighter 戰團<br />\n打算交之際佢話要check下份野<br />\n係我地前面仲有個男仔比佢check緊<br />\n點知佢check完個男仔話唔收啦因為過左5點<br />\n我地即刻打左個突<br />\n我地：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個西職員：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：但係我地準時黎架喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：但你地就到5點先黎而且我都無收過你地份野咁你地係咪遲丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係我地問題sorry可唔可以比我地四個交埋（無錯連個個比佢check嘅男仔都無收好似話有少少問題）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你地咁樣出黎做野唔得架喎！我頭先由搭九企左係到就係驚收唔到你地D form 你地遲交野比prof都唔會預咁忟水啦！你地遲交會點？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：比人扣分但都比我地交<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咁唔同講法架嘛你出到黎做野遲到就係遲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：但我地準時黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你地準時黎點解唔早D黎！你知唔知你地咁樣好無teamspirit（我都唔知關咩事）blah blah blah<br />\n我地四個企左係counter比佢屌左十幾分鐘，佢就話<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地走啦下年請早</span></span><br />\n個下我地四個真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔撚係啊比你屌完仲要無得交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a7bdf81ab3929fc8be093b2b6692da12319899","tid":302053,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"dead line 唔預早啲？"},{"pid":"356c1b5e82c861517dca62d7e34932def8e28b99","tid":302053,"uid":3206,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:55:36.000Z","msg":"平時受得氣多，人工又低，唔屌你地屌邊個呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 坻佢成世做低級職員"},{"pid":"fb46a1f262744033a6bc79226cc731dcd34204b0","tid":302053,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T05:58:34.000Z","msg":"不嬲垃圾"},{"pid":"74b03165317befdf210603e48f06261ce7716f98","tid":302053,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:01:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69f8254f1a6f49860a8dcc879fb8ae5bb0e5282f","tid":302053,"uid":27777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"不嬲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前叫佢開個班房門(星期六)<br />\n係到呢樣唔得個樣唔得多多聲氣<br />\n<br />\n打個電話比教自己既老師<br />\n一野就拎到條key開門"},{"pid":"1e822a12f495f9d55f2c65b7d0c6486d1c841b58","tid":302053,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T06:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>dead line 唔預早啲？</blockquote><br />\n我同我朋友都十五十六唔上唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢prog個網keep住有新proj<br />\n去到最後幾日我地先搵到我地想去嘅地方先話去啦<br />\n但我地都知我地衰仔<br />\n預到咁忟水交一過到去即刻講sorry咁遲<br />\n個一刻都預左無得交就算啦係自己問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse